data.title: Mark Woodforde
data.meta_description: Listen to this episode from Racquet's Rennae Stubbs Tennis Podcast on Spotify. data.text:
The Aussie legend joins Caitlin in the BNP Paribas x Racquet Kisoque to talk about his storied career, the resurgence of Aussie tennis (from Tommo to Rinky Hijikata), the places his gold medal has found itself recently, and the great strides made by his home slam—and second home slam, the BNP Paribas Open at Indian Wells.

Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
